        val desc: String?, // <p>Pachira, tree of money and luck</p>The money tree is a favorite of plant parents and pet parents. It is said that this green and living good luck charm brings positive energy and abundance to its owner.Bamboo palm<img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/%DA%AF%DB%8C%D8%A7%D9%87-%D9%BE%D8%A7%DA%86%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%DA%AF%D9%84-768x937.jpg'>If you're looking for a classic palm with a tropical twist, check out the Bamboo Palm. This non-toxic houseplant is not dangerous for your dog or cat and gives your home or apartment a homely feel.<p>Pineapple Bromeliad</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/%D9%86%D8%AE%D9%84-%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C%DA%A9%D8%A7-%D8%B1%D9%88%DB%8C-%D9%85%DB%8C%D8%B2-768x922.jpg'>Pineapple is a beautiful and amazing plant and your loved ones can live together without any threat. This plant produces one pineapple fruit per plant. Although this species is not grown for food consumption, it is still not dangerous for pets.<p>neon prayer hall</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%AE%DA%86%D9%87-%D8%A2%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%B3-800x801.jpg'>The neon prayer plant has striking marigold green leaves that are an eye-catching addition to any room. Best of all, these attractive plants are non-toxic to both cats and dogs.<p>Ponytail palm</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bloomscape_neon-prayer-plant_clay-853x1024-1-768x922.jpg'>If you like to travel and sightseeing, Horsetail Palm is suitable for you. Because this plant is strong and resistant to drought and requires minimal attention and does not pose a danger to any of your furry family members who live next to it.<p>Blue star fern</p>The beautiful and dramatic Blue Star Fern will grace your space while also being safe for pets. This beauty adapts to any climate and can grow quickly in places with indirect light.<p>Red Prayer Plant</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bloomscape_red-prayer-plant_charcoal-1024x1229-1-768x922.jpg'>Choose a plant of your red variety. Like its neon counterpart, the beautiful red prayer plant requires little maintenance and is safe and suitable for loved ones<p>Bromeliad Aechmea Pink</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bloomscape_bromeliad-aechmea-pink_slate-853x1024-1-768x922.jpg'>For a beautiful, flowering plant, consider Bromeliad Aechmea Pink. This bromeliad has bright pink blooms and does not pose a health risk to your pets.<p>Prickly pear cactus</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/%DA%A9%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%88%D8%B3-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%A8-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B2%D9%84-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%DA%AF%D9%84-768x922.jpg'>You don't have to give up your love of cacti when you bring a new pet into your home. Prickly pear cactus is a low-trouble, non-toxic plant, but be careful with its thorns.<p>Stromante Triostar</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bloomscape_stromanthe_triostar_large_clay-1024x1229-1-768x922.jpg'>The colorful Stromanthe Triostar has striking white, pink and green leaves and will add a vibrant pop of color to your home and best of all, it's safe for pets.<p>Summer bromeliad</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bloomscape_bromeliad-summer_small_indigo-1024x1229-1-768x922.jpg'>For a unique and beautiful plant that is also recommended for any home full of animals, with bright and cheerful magenta flowers, which require little maintenance and add warmth to your space.<p>Chinese fan palm</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/%D9%86%D8%AE%D9%84-%D9%BE%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85-%D9%81%D9%88%D9%86%DB%8C%DA%A9%D8%B3-800x961.jpg'>Chinese fan palm is a compact tropical plant that displays large, dramatic branches that look like folded paper fans. This gorgeous plant is non-toxic to the whole family, but beware that it has sharp thorns on its stems.<p>Individual Kalatha</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bloomscape_calathea-freddie_small_slate-1024x1229-1-768x922.jpg'>Be sure to get a beautiful individual Kalatia for your home. This attractive plant with a tropical appearance, consisting of bright green leaves and dark green stripes, will not pose a threat to your curious puppy or kitten.<p>Kangaroo Fern</p><img src='https://aloogol.ir/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Bloomscape_KangarooFernAlternate_Medium_Charcoal-1024x1280-1-768x960.jpg'>Always vibrant and easy to maintain, the kangaroo fern has unique deep green leaves and long, fuzzy roots called rhizomes that help the plant grow. Not only is this plant adaptable to most climates, but this stunning houseplant is safe for cats and dogs.
